; Coverage for amount.cc
; When a commodity already has COMMODITY_STYLE_DECIMAL_COMMA (established
; by a commodity directive), encountering a period with digit grouping
; that is not a multiple of 3 throws "Incorrect use of thousand-mark
; period". Here "1.23,00" has only 2 digits between period and comma.

commodity 1.000,00 EUR

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    1.23,00 EUR
    Assets:Cash

test bal -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 10:
While parsing posting:
  Expenses:Food    1.23,00 EUR
                   ^^^^^^^^^^^
Error: Incorrect use of thousand-mark period
end test
